The paper deals with a wireless relay network and proposes a statistical model based on Gaussian Processes to perform system identification. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT) or Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper also deals with optimization and computational efficiency, which could place it in the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category. The use of Bayesian methodology and algorithms for estimation suggest that the paper could also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
